<div class="system-visual decision-diagram" aria-label="Decision diagram for choosing one prompt, fixed steps, or a loop">
  <div class="system-bar">
    <span>simple test</span>
    <span class="system-bar-note">choose the smallest setup</span>
  </div>
  <div class="decision-body">
    <div class="decision-question">
      <span class="decision-dot"></span>
      <strong>Will the AI learn something after it tries?</strong>
    </div>

    <div class="decision-path path-single">
      <span class="verdict-chip vc-single">ONE PROMPT</span>
      <div>
        <strong>No new information</strong>
        <small>Ask once. Get one answer.</small>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="decision-path path-chain">
      <span class="verdict-chip vc-chain">FIXED STEPS</span>
      <div>
        <strong>The order is known</strong>
        <small>Do step 1, then step 2, then step 3.</small>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="decision-path path-loop">
      <span class="verdict-chip vc-loop">LOOP</span>
      <div>
        <strong>It needs feedback</strong>
        <small>Try, check what happened, then try again.</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
